DESCRIPTION:Join Campus Activities for our Spring Student Retreat  a chanc
 e to step away from campus\, connect with other students\, and enjoy a da
 y filled with activities\, good food\, and a refreshing change of scenery
 . This trip is designed to help you relax\, recharge\, and make new memor
 ies while participating in group experiences and social opportunities thr
 oughout the day.\nThe trip is open to current Bloomfield/Montclair State 
 students only. Spots are limited and available on a first-come\, first-se
 rved basis.\nA $5 (cash only) reservation fee is required to secure your 
 spot at the time of sign-up.\nTransportation will be provided\, and the b
 us will depart from and return to the Bloomfield Campus. All meals are in
 cluded\, and some snacks will be provided. Students are encouraged to wea
 r comfortable clothing and shoes suitable for a full day of activities.\n
 Additional trip details\, including itinerary information and preparation
  instructions\, will be shared with students once their registration and 
 reservation are confirmed.\n \nTo sign up you must go to the Bloomfield C
 ampus - Campus Activities located in Talbott Hall \n\nHosted by: Campus A
 ctivities at Bloomfield\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https:
 //montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12242200
