DESCRIPTION:The Brotherhood / La Hermanidad General Body Meetings\nJoin Th
 e Brotherhood / La Hermanidad every Tuesday from 2:00 PM – 3:30 PM for ou
 r weekly General Body Meetings. This is a dedicated space for Black and B
 rown men to come together in unity\, build community\, and engage in mean
 ingful conversations that promote personal\, academic\, and professional 
 growth.\nEach week\, we create an environment centered on brotherhood\, e
 mpowerment\, and accountability—discussing real-life topics\, supporting 
