DESCRIPTION:Cali Midweek Series: Chamber Music Recital\nA chamber music co
 ncert at the Cali School of Music unites ensembles from across the entire
  program. As part of the vibrant Midweek Series—free and open to the publ
 ic at 2pm—students from strings\, winds\, brass\, percussion\, piano\, an
 d voice perform a diverse program that highlights collaboration and the r
 ich musical community of the school. \n---------------------\nCali Midwee
 k Concerts 2025-26Wednesdays at 2 PMChapin Hall\, Leshowitz Recital Hall\
 nFREE ADMISSION!\nJoin us for the Cali Midweek Concerts at Montclair Stat
 e University’s John J. Cali School of Music\, where we bring a diverse ar
 ray of musical performances and educational events every Wednesday at 2PM
  in Leshowitz Recital Hall\, Chapin Hall. Our concert series showcases th
 e immense talent within our faculty\, students\, and esteemed guest artis
 ts.\n\nHosted by: The College of the Arts\n\nAdditional Information can b
 e found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12358396
