DESCRIPTION:The AI literacy for educators designed to support educators in
  building a strong\, practical understanding of artificial intelligence i
 n educational contexts. This workshop will help educators understand foun
 dational AI concepts\, critically evaluate AI tools and outputs\, recogni
 ze how bias and inequity can emerge in AI systems\, and examine the ethic
 al and societal implications of AI use in teaching and learning. Particip
 ants will also explore strategies for working with AI responsibly\, empha
