DESCRIPTION:The Turning Point USA Chapter at Montclair State University in
 vites students\, faculty\, and guests to attend its End-of-Semester Gala\
 , an evening dedicated to celebrating leadership\, civic engagement\, and
  open dialogue on campus. This formal event will bring together members o
 f the university community for dinner\, music\, and thoughtfully curated 
 programming that reflects the importance of free expression\, personal re
 sponsibility\, and respectful discourse. The evening will feature keynote
  and student remarks\, recognition of student leadership\, and opportunit
 ies for networking and community building in a professional and welcoming
  environment. Guests will enjoy a seated dinner\, a DJ and dance floor\, 
 and designated photo opportunities throughout the night. This gala serves
  as a capstone celebration of the chapter’s activities throughout the sem
 ester and provides an inclusive space for reflection\, conversation\, and
  connection among students from diverse academic and personal backgrounds
 .\n\nHosted by: Turning Point USA \n\nAdditional Information can be found
  at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12293486
